but we're not supposed

22:25.256 --> 22:27.302
to say "Chinaman" anymore.

22:27.346 --> 22:29.130
- Well, didn't get that memo.

22:29.173 --> 22:31.959
- Your script uses it 34 times.

22:32.002 --> 22:34.135
All in reference
to George Takei,

22:34.178 --> 22:36.050
who is of Japanese descent.

22:36.093 --> 22:38.095
[club whacking ball]

22:40.359 --> 22:42.404
