The three magic wishes!

22:48.323 --> 22:50.543
- We don't need them.

22:50.586 --> 22:52.240
- [clears throat]

22:54.198 --> 22:58.681
Kap... [grunts]
Mulligan.

22:58.725 --> 23:02.772
The three wishes are the crux
of the whole piece.

23:02.816 --> 23:04.644
- They're a little pat.

23:07.298 --> 23:09.431
- [grunts]
Mulligan.

23:09.475 --> 23:12.260
They're not pat.
They're classics.

23:12.303 --> 23:15.045
[grunts] And they speak
to the child in all of us.

23:15.089 --> 23:17.221
The secret longing
that we all have.

23:17.265 --> 23:19.136
Surely even you...
[grunts]

23:19.180 --> 23:22.618
Must have some
unfulfilled wishes.

23:22.662 --> 23:24.794
- [laughs]
Please, Sonny.

23:24.838 --> 23:27.231
I run the third-largest network
in the nation.

23:27.275 --> 23:29.320
I have more money than I know
what to do with.

23:29.364 --> 23:32.236
My wife and mistresses
are, well, not friends,

23:32.280 --> 23:33.673
but on good terms.

23:33.716 --> 23:36.153
I have everything
a man could wish for.

23:36.197 --> 23:39.200
- What about the things a man
shouldn't wish for?

23:39.243 --> 23:40.593
[clears throat]

23:40.636 --> 23:42.508
[ominous music]

23:42.551 --> 23:44.379
[club whacks ball]

23:44.423 --> 23:47.513
You know, the ones
that keep him awake at night,

23:47.556 --> 23:49.645
or come to him in his dreams.

23:49.689 --> 23:53.780
I mean, surely even you
must have one of those, Kap.

23:53.823 --> 23:56.347
♪

23:56.391 --> 23:57.523
- Whoa.

23:57.566 --> 23:59.612
Ooh-la-la.

23:59.655 --> 24:03.050
This room is très exotique.

24:03.093 --> 24:04.443
- Well, thank you.

24:04.486 --> 24:07.707
I'll pass the compliment
to Otho, my decorator.

24:07.750 --> 24:10.057
- [gasps]
You can see me?

24:10.100 --> 24:12.233
- Well, of course,
my little piglet.

24:12.276 --> 24:14.496
Haven't we met before?

24:14.540 --> 24:17.673
Riding the green fairy
with Price Rainier

24:17.717 --> 24:19.283
at The Coconut Grove?

24:19.327 --> 24:21.547
- The Green Fairy.
Green Fairy.

24:21.590 --> 24:23.113
I don't know who that is.

24:23.157 --> 24:25.072
- Well, butter-bean,
who do you know?

24:25.115 --> 24:27.683
- Uh, do you know
Hailey Hansen?

24:27.727 --> 24:29.250
- I can't say that I do.

24:29.293 --> 24:31.252
- Oh, we were together
for ten years,

24:31.295 --> 24:35.125
but that ended recently.
- Aww, there, there.

24:35.169 --> 24:37.476
Well, you came
to the right place, darling.

24:37.519 --> 24:39.869
Oh, Bebe knows all about--

24:39.913 --> 24:42.785
I mean, allabout heartbreak.

24:42.829 --> 24:45.440
La grande tristesse.

24:45.484 --> 24:48.617
- I have a new partner now,
but it's not the same.

24:48.661 --> 24:50.663
He can be a real prickly pear.

24:50.706 --> 24:52.491
- "He"?

24:52.534 --> 24:55.711
Oh. Well, that's okay.
Bebe's open-minded.

24:55.755 --> 24:57.496
- I mean, I care about him,
I do.

24:57.539 --> 25:00.107
